":\"Dog Parks in Burlington, NC\"}],\"$undefined\",[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-description\",\"children\":\"From the shaded trails of Cedarock Park to local community runs, Burlington provides a welcoming environment for dogs in the heart of Alamance County.\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-rich-description\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"rich-description-paragraph\",\"children\":[\"Burlington, NC, serves as a central hub in the Piedmont region, offering dog owners access to expansive parks and well-maintained trails. Key destinations include the \",[\"$\",\"$L12\",\"1\",{\"href\":\"https://www.burlingtonnc.gov/237/City-Park\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"Burlington City Park\"}],null,\", known for its family-friendly atmosphere and walking paths perfect for leashed exploration. For off-leash play, the Burlington Animal Services Center operates a popular dog park featuring separate areas for different breed sizes. The city also offers access to the \",[\"$\",\"$L12\",\"4\",{\"href\":\"https://thehaw.org/\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"Haw River Trail\"}],null,\", providing miles of scenic riverside hiking for active dogs and their owners. Our \",[\"$\",\"$L12\",\"7\",{\"href\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/cities/burlington-nc#park-directory\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"Burlington directory\"}],null,\" highlights these accessible recreational gems.\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"rich-description-paragraph\",\"children\":[\"Responsible pet ownership is central to the Burlington community, with local ordinances requiring rabies vaccinations and adherence to leash laws in public areas. The city actively supports pet adoption and welfare through its Animal Services division. Dog-friendly events often take place at the Burlington Arboretum, where leashed pets can enjoy the gardens. For those looking to understand regional pet policies or find training tips, our \",[\"$\",\"$L12\",\"1\",{\"href\":\"/blog\",\"target\":\"$undefined\",\"rel\":\"$undefined\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"blog\"}],null,\" offers valuable insights. Burlington's blend of municipal support and natural beauty makes it a reliable and enjoyable home for canine companions.\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta-row\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L30\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta primary\",\"targetId\":\"park-directory\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-list-check\"}],\"Browse directory\"]}],[\"$\",\"$L30\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta ghost\",\"targetId\":\"map-and-neighborhoods\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-geo-alt\"}],\"Open map\"]}],[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/list-your-park\",\"className\":\"hero-cta text-link\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-plus-circle\"}],\"Submit a park\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-footnotes\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",\"Data refreshed weekly\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-sparkles\"}],\" \",\"Data refreshed weekly\"]}],[\"$\",\"span\",\"Live availability coming soon\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-sparkles\"}],\" \",\"Live availability coming soon\"]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-hero-visual\",\"children\":\"$L31\"}]]}]}],\"$L32\",\"$L33\",\"$L34\",\"$L35\",\"$L36\",\"$L37\",\"$undefined\",\"$L38\",\"$L39\",\"$L3a\",\"$L3b\",\"$L3c\"]}]\n2b:[\"$\",\"footer\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-new\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-container\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-grid\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-column\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h4\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-heading\",\"children\":\"Indoor